# Kansas City Chiefs: Championships
[← Back to Home](README.md)

The Chiefs have won multiple Super Bowls and AFC titles.

## Super Bowl Wins

### Super Bowl IV
- Beat the Vikings
- Score: 23–7
- MVP: Len Dawson

### Super Bowl LIV (2020)
- Beat the 49ers
- Score: 31–20
- MVP: Patrick Mahomes

### Super Bowl LVII (2023)
- Beat the Eagles
- Score: 38–35
- MVP: Patrick Mahomes

## AFC Championships
| Year | Result | Opponent |
|-------|--------|------------|
| 2019 | Win | Titans |
| 2020 | Win | Bills |
| 2022 | Win | Bengals |
| 2023 | Win | Ravens |

The Chiefs today are known for being one of the top teams in the NFL.
